Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:13.20,0:02:20.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(190,233)\fs24\fnsimhei\bord0\shad1\1c&Hffffff&\fade(255,0,255,0,1500,6300,7300)}祖父與孫子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:13.20,0:02:16.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,至少今天一天…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:21.50,0:02:23.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你祖父嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:23.30,0:02:26.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是我媽那邊的突然說想看看我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:26.70,0:02:28.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以就臨時通知我…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:28.60,0:02:31.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,今晚可以讓他在這裏過夜嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:31.90,0:02:33.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你在客氣什麼啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:33.80,0:02:39.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,既然是阿優的外公\N當然沒什麼行不行的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:39.10,0:02:41.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他平常就是個大忙人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:41.80,0:02:46.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,老實說至今為止我也沒見過幾次面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:46.00,0:02:48.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對了 你們知道嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:48.80,0:02:51.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那個近衛工業的會長
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:51.80,0:02:53.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,近衛優一郎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:55.50,0:02:58.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,知道 他是誰呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:58.00,0:02:59.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我外公
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:13.70,0:03:17.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,阿優 好久不見了啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:17.10,0:03:19.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,外公 真是好久不見了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:19.30,0:03:20.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:21.20,0:03:24.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這位是住在這裏工作的女傭麻幌
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:24.50,0:03:26.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,跟她的妹妹美奈和
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:27.70,0:03:29.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你…你好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:32.20,0:03:34.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是個好孩子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:35.80,0:03:38.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,簡直就跟新家一樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:38.60,0:03:43.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在麻幌來之前還被說成跟像鬼屋呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:46.80,0:03:50.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這裏也全都是麻幌整理的…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:52.40,0:03:56.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你好像工作地很快樂呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:56.20,0:04:00.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不是的 我不是抱著輕鬆的心情在做事…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:00.00,0:04:02.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為這是我的業務啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:02.50,0:04:04.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,說不上什麼高興不高興的…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:04.70,0:04:10.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,工作未必全是做的不愉快的吧 麻幌
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:10.10,0:04:13.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對…您說的是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:13.50,0:04:14.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我很高興
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:22.40,0:04:24.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好香的味道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:24.80,0:04:26.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在哪？讓我嘗嘗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:26.70,0:04:29.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,現在還不行喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:29.90,0:04:31.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有什麼不好嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:31.50,0:04:32.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:32.30,0:04:33.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一點就好…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:33.90,0:04:35.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,爺爺？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:35.70,0:04:38.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不可以一直這樣！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:38.50,0:04:40.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就讓我吃一點就好了嘛～
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:40.80,0:04:42.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拜託啦拜託啦～
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:42.00,0:04:44.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,請不要這樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:46.50,0:04:49.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還不夠鹹啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:49.20,0:04:52.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這樣就不能整合素材的味道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:52.60,0:04:55.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,才做到一半當然不行啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:55.80,0:04:58.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,口味不合是理所當然的吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:58.60,0:05:00.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還在最硬啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:00.80,0:05:04.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,做這道料理 鹽味是最後才來調節的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:04.00,0:05:06.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,做好的料理我不管
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:06.20,0:05:08.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,插手正在調理的料理
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:08.60,0:05:10.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,無論是誰我都無法原諒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:10.80,0:05:14.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對女傭而言 廚房就是自己的戰場
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:14.70,0:05:18.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在這種地方粗心大意是你的過錯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:18.00,0:05:19.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,若是硬要強詞奪理的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:19.50,0:05:21.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是絕對不會饒恕的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:21.10,0:05:23.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有趣 要來就來吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:23.80,0:05:25.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐 加油
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:28.70,0:05:31.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等等 麻幌你在做什麼啊？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:31.10,0:05:32.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,外公你也是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:32.70,0:05:34.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,阿優你給我閃開
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:49.40,0:05:53.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,麻幌 再怎麼樣你都做的太過火了啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:53.00,0:05:53.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,外公
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:53.90,0:05:59.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我所追求的就是這個啊！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:59.40,0:06:01.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我在懂事前就失去所有親人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:01.90,0:06:05.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嘗盡人間辛酸而成長的我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:05.40,0:06:09.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我含恨對著血紅的夕陽如此發誓
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:09.20,0:06:11.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我一定要向上爬
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:11.10,0:06:14.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,總有一天要站在世界的頂端給大家瞧瞧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:14.40,0:06:17.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,然後…在我達到這一天的時候…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:17.40,0:06:24.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我的身邊的人都畏懼我\N光會對我必恭必敬
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:24.10,0:06:28.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是只有她不一樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:28.50,0:06:34.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,把有著巨大財富和權力的我\N看作一個普通男人來愛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:34.90,0:06:36.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,美紗…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:36.70,0:06:39.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊 我美麗的妻子啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:39.90,0:06:43.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,全部都是騙人的 不要相信他就好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:43.10,0:06:45.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你說什麼啊？現在精采的才正要來呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:45.80,0:06:47.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要打斷我啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:47.70,0:06:51.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,外公你不是很久以前就跟我說\N你老家很有錢的嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:51.90,0:06:56.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而且還聽說奶奶是因為\N你在外面亂搞被發現才離家出走的不是嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:56.50,0:06:59.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,光會記無聊事情的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:59.30,0:07:00.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,說中了？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:01.70,0:07:03.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:06.70,0:07:08.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這是？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:08.30,0:07:10.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在女人堆中只有一個男的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:10.40,0:07:12.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也就是說…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:12.00,0:07:14.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,阿優 你還真受歡迎啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:14.50,0:07:16.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很受歡迎不是嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:16.70,0:07:19.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只是個中學生就這麼受歡迎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:19.10,0:07:20.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這麼的受歡迎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:20.90,0:07:21.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,絕對不能原諒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:21.80,0:07:23.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,早安啊美裏同學
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:23.90,0:07:27.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我今天、今天一定要毫不保留地
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:27.10,0:07:29.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,讓你知道「那個世界」的一切…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:32.60,0:07:34.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,阿優 這位是誰？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:34.70,0:07:36.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,班主任老師
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:36.10,0:07:38.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:38.00,0:07:42.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,美裏同學 這個奇怪的老頭子是誰？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:42.80,0:07:44.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是我外公
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:44.70,0:07:48.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,阿優 你到底是怎麼樣的中學生啊？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:48.70,0:07:50.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼怎麼樣啊…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:50.40,0:07:54.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過還真是豐滿\N而且如此的美妙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:54.70,0:07:56.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我也要一起來～
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:56.80,0:07:59.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,外公住手啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:01.70,0:08:02.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我認為H…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:02.90,0:08:04.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是不行的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:08.60,0:08:10.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:10.20,0:08:12.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,午安
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:12.30,0:08:15.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,流河老師？你有什麼事嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:15.40,0:08:20.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我醒來之後就看到這東西放在我上衣裏…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:21.80,0:08:23.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,寫的真草
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:23.70,0:08:27.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,『請把這張紙帶到美裏家來…』
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:27.80,0:08:30.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,『給你好東西』
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:30.00,0:08:31.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這到底是什麼？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:31.50,0:08:35.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不擅長用鉛筆寫字
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:35.40,0:08:38.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,史萊修？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:38.60,0:08:44.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,既然好不容易來一趟 就請他吃頓好的吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:44.10,0:08:45.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:50.50,0:08:51.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,幹什麼？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:51.60,0:08:54.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你長的還真英俊啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:54.20,0:08:58.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,老師長的這麼英俊想必一定很受歡迎吧？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:58.70,0:08:59.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,受歡迎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:59.90,0:09:03.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不找受歡迎的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:08.00,0:09:10.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是難得來了一起喝一杯怎樣？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:10.70,0:09:13.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很可惜 我很難接受
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:13.90,0:09:17.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼？你是說我的酒不能喝嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:17.20,0:09:19.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,您似乎不曉得
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:19.30,0:09:23.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這個國家未成年是禁止喝酒的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:23.50,0:09:26.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那跟你又有什麼關係？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:26.50,0:09:27.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大有關係
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:27.60,0:09:30.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為我才三歲而已
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:30.40,0:09:33.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你是醉的一塌糊塗了？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:35.60,0:09:39.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,其實他是聖者的機器人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:39.80,0:09:44.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很意外的\N其實他是個單細胞笨蛋啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:44.90,0:09:46.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,史萊修…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:46.40,0:09:49.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你還真像一隻貓啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:50.60,0:09:53.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,應該憐憫老人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:53.90,0:09:55.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,…沒辦法了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:57.00,0:09:58.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,太好了太好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:58.10,0:10:01.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,給你之前我已經搖了100多下了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:01.50,0:10:04.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是對不起…流河老師
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:04.20,0:10:06.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我外公醉了一塌糊塗…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:06.80,0:10:10.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們必須憐憫老人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:10.70,0:10:12.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,請用
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:12.70,0:10:15.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:21.50,0:10:23.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,美奈和 怎麼了嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:23.70,0:10:26.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,請再給我一條毛巾
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:26.20,0:10:34.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要輸給年輕人…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:34.40,0:10:36.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真受不了他
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:36.30,0:10:40.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是真的是個有趣的外公啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:40.50,0:10:45.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對啊 我都不知道阿優有這樣的外公
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:45.00,0:10:48.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我也想要那樣的外公呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:48.00,0:10:52.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你說這話是什麼意思呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:52.60,0:10:56.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,聽進去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:56.70,0:10:58.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我真的沒有其他的意思啦
