Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:08.00,0:11:10.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,多謝招待
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:10.90,0:11:11.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再見
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:11.70,0:11:15.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要不要 美裏同學我還要喝～
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:15.20,0:11:17.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,老師清醒點
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:17.30,0:11:20.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那來個告別之吻
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:20.40,0:11:22.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,H是不行的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:27.00,0:11:30.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們今天的工作已經做完了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:30.80,0:11:34.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,請允許我們洗澡休息
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:34.10,0:11:36.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,今天一天辛苦了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:36.50,0:11:38.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,辛苦了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:42.40,0:11:45.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那我們也去吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:45.00,0:11:46.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,去哪里？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:46.30,0:11:49.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,廢話 當然是去偷窺啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:49.60,0:11:51.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,偷窺？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:51.40,0:11:56.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,本來還在等你邀請我的\N不過我已經忍不住了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:56.10,0:11:57.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我先去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:57.10,0:12:00.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等一下 不要做這種事情啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:00.80,0:12:04.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,阿優 你不用跟我太客氣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:04.00,0:12:05.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還是說你有意見？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:05.90,0:12:08.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有這麼可愛的美人姐妹在這個家裏
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:08.30,0:12:11.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你該不會是不想讓我看吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:11.50,0:12:14.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我可不打算去偷窺
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:14.40,0:12:16.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:16.50,0:12:19.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不是不瞭解你害羞的心情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:19.50,0:12:21.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是要坦率 我的孫子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:21.50,0:12:26.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要是偷窺一定會傷害到美奈和跟麻幌的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:26.50,0:12:29.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,說的真是漂亮
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:29.20,0:12:32.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那麼只要不被發現就不會有人受傷了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:32.60,0:12:36.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這樣做又有什麼兩樣啊！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:37.40,0:12:39.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,該怎麼說才好呢…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:39.90,0:12:43.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不管怎麼說不行的事就是不行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:43.90,0:12:47.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你應該也有些黃色書刊吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:50.00,0:12:51.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,當然有啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:51.50,0:12:54.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雖然全都被麻幌沒收了…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:54.60,0:12:58.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你應該沒看過真的女性裸體吧？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:58.60,0:12:59.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我早就看過了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:59.90,0:13:02.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,跟麻幌一起洗澡的那個時候…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:04.40,0:13:08.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,跟…跟麻幌一起洗澡…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:08.90,0:13:10.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真會逗我笑…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:10.80,0:13:12.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,原來不是沒看過啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:12.80,0:13:15.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,原來如此…一起啊…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:15.10,0:13:18.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那跟偷窺跟這比起來\N根本就沒什麼大不了了嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:18.30,0:13:19.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不是啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:19.50,0:13:22.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是麻幌說要幫我洗背擅自進來的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:22.90,0:13:26.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,事實上我馬上就昏倒了所以記不太清楚…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:26.50,0:13:29.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在那之後就沒有過這種事情了…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:29.40,0:13:32.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那你當時沒看仔細嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:33.60,0:13:36.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那個時候我只是嚇了一大跳…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:36.50,0:13:38.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這樣啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:38.70,0:13:41.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,女人是個好東西喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:41.60,0:13:43.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很溫暖喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:43.00,0:13:46.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,既水嫩又光滑…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:46.00,0:13:49.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你難道從沒想過\N『要好好看一下就好了』嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:49.40,0:13:52.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,當然想看啊 但是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:52.10,0:13:55.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你說你想看對吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:56.40,0:13:59.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快 踩在我肩上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:59.30,0:14:00.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:00.20,0:14:03.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,老的要讓著點年輕人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:03.10,0:14:04.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快踩上來吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:04.30,0:14:06.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那我就不好意思了…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:21.80,0:14:24.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,乳房靠近點就有女人味了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:30.20,0:14:32.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好空虛…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:34.40,0:14:36.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還是不能這樣做啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:36.90,0:14:39.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要叫這麼大聲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:39.70,0:14:42.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你們在做什麼啊！！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:42.30,0:14:44.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,燙燙燙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:44.90,0:14:49.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不是說了N遍『H是不行的』了嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:49.40,0:14:54.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你哪里像是阿優的模範？\N盡教唆他變態的事情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:54.30,0:14:55.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對…了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:55.40,0:14:57.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什…麼？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:57.30,0:15:00.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我聽說你曾經自己脫的光光的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:00.90,0:15:03.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,然後跟阿優一起洗澡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:03.20,0:15:07.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,難道這就不是H了嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:07.10,0:15:11.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我也覺得我做的太過份了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:11.60,0:15:14.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以我也有反省…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:14.40,0:15:15.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,反省嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:15.80,0:15:17.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我有反省了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:18.20,0:15:19.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對…了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:19.60,0:15:21.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什…麼？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:21.50,0:15:24.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,話說回來美奈和還是個見習中的女傭吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:24.80,0:15:29.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不讓那個孩子跟阿優一起洗澡是因為倫理觀吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:29.90,0:15:31.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,當然啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:31.90,0:15:34.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我的目標就是成為完美的女傭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:34.90,0:15:36.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這樣啊…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:36.50,0:15:39.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那麼在一起的時候究竟發什麼火？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:39.50,0:15:42.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你腦子裏又是想著什麼H的事？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:42.10,0:15:44.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,咦？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:44.10,0:15:46.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,老實說！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:46.00,0:15:47.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,說…什麼？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:47.50,0:15:51.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,老是想著什麼HH的女傭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:51.50,0:15:56.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,其實你自己才是最H的不是嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:59.20,0:16:01.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那我們要睡了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:01.50,0:16:03.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good Night～
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:04.50,0:16:06.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,H…我H…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:06.70,0:16:07.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐 我們也睡吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:11.50,0:16:14.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,阿優 你還醒著嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:14.50,0:16:17.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,麻幌已經睡了嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:17.90,0:16:19.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要去夜襲嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:19.30,0:16:21.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,外公 不要再做這種事了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:21.30,0:16:22.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你到底是來做什麼的？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:22.80,0:16:24.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,開玩笑的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:27.70,0:16:32.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,白天的那些女孩子包括那個戴眼鏡的老師
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:32.40,0:16:35.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那裏面有你中意的女孩子嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:35.20,0:16:41.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,據我觀察大家都很喜歡你喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:41.10,0:16:45.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,式條老師是老師
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:45.10,0:16:49.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,美雪跟凜她們是從幼稚園就在一起的青梅竹馬
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:49.60,0:16:55.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不喜歡大家弄得不開心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:55.80,0:16:58.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你還真認真啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:58.50,0:17:02.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,認真是好事情 但是如果在長大之前
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:02.10,0:17:05.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就那麼在意一些小事情不太好吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:07.10,0:17:09.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,老是巧妙的敷衍應付他人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:09.80,0:17:14.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你這樣子不會太過份了嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:14.30,0:17:17.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這種事情…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:17.40,0:17:19.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我可不想被外公這樣說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:19.80,0:17:21.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,阿優 聽好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:21.40,0:17:23.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一個男人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:23.20,0:17:28.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只有知道自己的不足\N才能變得完美
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:28.20,0:17:30.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你這樣子得過且過下去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:30.50,0:17:34.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,最後也只會變成一個無趣的男人而已
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:44.50,0:17:47.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,您不再多留一會嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:47.80,0:17:52.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我還有很多菜想請您吃
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:52.20,0:17:53.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我啊…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:53.90,0:17:58.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你也好 阿優也好 看你們都平安就放心了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:58.50,0:18:02.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒想到首領會是阿優的外公
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:02.10,0:18:04.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我真是嚇了一大跳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:04.20,0:18:08.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這可是最高機密喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:08.10,0:18:13.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不在了之後 美奈和就請你照顧了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:13.80,0:18:17.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你這樣擔心會不會太早了一點？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:17.10,0:18:23.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那孩子的內心的大半部分\N好像還被什麼可怕的事佔據著
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:23.60,0:18:29.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是在那深處\N我能看到她美麗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:29.90,0:18:36.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在我身邊不久會發生什麼事情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:36.40,0:18:40.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雖然那可能是非常危險的事情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:40.10,0:18:41.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是我無論如何…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:41.60,0:18:45.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,都想拯救美奈和那孩子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:45.10,0:18:47.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我真的很奇怪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:47.40,0:18:52.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我一直都認為出生之後\N會死亡是理所當然的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:52.10,0:18:55.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是現在我卻很怕死亡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:55.50,0:18:57.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那太好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:57.60,0:19:03.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那就表示你已經找到\N你不想失去的東西了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:09.10,0:19:14.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果知道這點 也就沒什麼遺憾的了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:16.60,0:19:19.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,美奈和也要多多保重啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:19.00,0:19:20.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:20.40,0:19:23.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,麻幌小姐 阿優就拜託你照顧了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:23.50,0:19:24.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:24.50,0:19:25.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好的…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:25.50,0:19:30.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我要是一直直接叫你的名字 阿優可是會吃醋的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:30.50,0:19:32.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,阿優
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:32.50,0:19:34.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要成為好男人喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:42.10,0:19:48.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,話說回來 為什麼外公現在才突然要來看我呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:48.30,0:19:51.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他應該很忙的啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:51.60,0:19:56.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大概是不久之後 決定著聖者跟地球人的未來的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:56.00,0:19:58.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,命運之日來臨的緣故吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:58.50,0:20:01.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以在那天來之前
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:01.10,0:20:03.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,首領想再一次…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:03.40,0:20:06.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,來看看我們吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:14.80,0:20:19.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這樣子只有降低主電腦的主電源了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:19.00,0:20:20.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那樣太亂來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:20.60,0:20:23.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,會怎樣我可不知道啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:32.90,0:20:36.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,教授 到處都引起大騷動了喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:36.60,0:20:41.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,現在只能將收集到的檔案再構成 作成試驗樣品了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:41.80,0:20:43.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是什麼檔案呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:43.60,0:20:45.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,說什麼廢話
